<h1> FAQs </h1>
<h2> How long does the hat take to make? </h2>
<p> The basic "beanie" takes about an hour to make. It depends on the amount of colours that you want to have in the hat. The other hats take around a day to make.</p>
<h2> How long does it take to send? </h2>
<p> It depends on the postage that you have selected but it should arrive in around 2-3 days after ordering. </p>
<h2> How many colours can I have in the hat? </h2>
<p> You can have as many as you like! </p>
<h2> Why is there a difference in the cost? </h2>
<p> The different costs reflect how much wool is being used. The larger the hat the more the price will be. </p>

